        {
            "title": "德昌電機發盈警 料截至今年3月底止全年純利跌21%至25%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德昌電機(00179)發盈警，預期截至今年3月底止年度股東應佔溢利將跌至介乎1.97億至2.07億美元，按年倒退21%至25%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"德昌電機官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/00179.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"德昌電機官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/00179.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">德昌電機官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司指出，期內盈利倒退是受多項因素綜合影響所致，包括分銷及行政員工成本、外匯變動對營運開支之影響、索償與賠償撥備及其他營運項目的上升，使淨溢利下跌約12%至16%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，由於就過去一項收購確認的無形資產錄得非現金減值，以及若干投資的公平值按年出現不利變動，亦影響期內利潤。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15903466-%e5%be%b7%e6%98%8c%e9%9b%bb%e6%a9%9f%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e8%ad%a6-%e6%96%99%e6%88%aa%e8%87%b3%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b43%e6%9c%88%e5%ba%95%e6%ad%a2%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c21%e8%87%b325",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250528_FI_source-web_00179.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-22 08:54:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "範式智能折讓近12%配股籌15.66億元 主要用於異構算力設備",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">範式智能(06682)今早公布，擬配售3880萬股集資15.66億元；配股價40.36元，較該股昨天收市價45.84元折讓約11.95%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：範式智能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230928_FI_source-web_06682.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：範式智能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230928_FI_source-web_06682.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：範式智能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股前5個交易日平均收市價42.95元計，配股價較之折讓6.03%；以該股前30個交易日平均收市價37.93元計，配股價則有溢價約6.39%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資淨額約15.56億元，其中約80%用於推進基於異構GPU的異構AI算力設備，為該公司的API業務提供基礎設施；約20%用於全球業務擴張及在收購支持新興業務的技術服務提供商，當中包括具身智能及智能設備領域。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15903439-%e7%af%84%e5%bc%8f%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e8%bf%9112%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c15-66%e5%84%84%e5%85%83-%e4%b8%bb%e8%a6%81%e7%94%a8%e6%96%bc%e7%95%b0%e6%a7%8b%e7%ae%97%e5%8a%9b%e8%a8%ad",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260326_FI_source-web_06682.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-22 08:45:07",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "ASMPT首季經調整盈利升2.04倍 料次季收入升約37%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ASMPT(00522)公布，今年首季經調整盈利2.63億元，按年升2.04倍；料次季收入介乎5.4億至6億美元之間，以中位數5.7億元計按年升37%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：ASMPT官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230726_FI_-source_web_ASMPT.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：ASMPT官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230726_FI_-source_web_ASMPT.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：ASMPT官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述經調整盈利是按非香港財務報告準則計量；若按香港財報準則，首季公司持有人應佔盈利2.54億元，按年增2.03倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若單計持續經營業務，首季經調整盈利3.35億元，按年升1.94倍；經調整經營利潤3.96億元，增長1.07倍；經調整毛利率39.5%，則較去年同期減少151點子。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以香港財報準則計，首季持續經營業務盈利3.24億元，按年升1.93倍；經營利潤3.85億元，增長1.06倍；毛利率39.5%，亦較去年同期減少150點子。銷售收入39.67億元(5.08億美元)，按年升32%，勝市場預期；新增訂單總額56.73億元(7.27億美元)，按年增71.6%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司指出，旗下多款產品受惠於AI技術的迭代，推動強勁需求。季度新增訂單總額超出預期，表面貼裝技術解決方案分部新增訂單總額創新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：ASMPT官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240716_FI_source-web_00552.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：ASMPT官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240716_FI_source-web_00552.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：ASMPT官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ASMPT預期，半導體解決方案分部將推動次季銷售收入增長，公司兩個業務分部的新增訂單總額將維持高位，而表面貼裝技術解決方案分部則或因高基數效應而按季下降。展望未來，AI驅動的結構性需求預期將於2026年支持整體半導體解決方案分部及表面貼裝技術解決方案分部的銷售收入增長。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司進一步指出，雖然中東地區持續的地緣政治局勢尚未對公司產生任何重大影響，但管理層亦意識到不確定性依舊存在。相信憑藉其全球布局，將能靈活應對任何潛在影響，並繼續密切關注局勢發展並按需要靈活應變。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15903391-asmpt%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%872-04%e5%80%8d-%e6%96%99%e6%ac%a1%e5%ad%a3%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%8437",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230724_FI_source-web_00522-ASMPT.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-22 08:35:19",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期低水逾130點 重磅港股ADR普偏低收逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時12分跌110點或0.41%，報26351點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報26227點，較香港上日現貨收市低259點或0.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣509.8元，較上日香港收市低9.2元或1.77%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣132.5元，較上日香港收市低3.78元或2.77%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣85.1元，較上日香港收市低1.33元或1.53%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣119.5元，較上日香港收市低3.5元或2.84%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣31.8元，較上日香港收市低0.62元或1.92%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣142元，較上日香港收市低1.74元或1.21%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣82.5元，較上日香港收市低0.34元或0.41%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣414.6元，較上日香港收市低2.63元或0.63%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣61.1元，較上日香港收市低0.33元或0.54%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.9元，較上日香港收市低0.05元或0.58%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報26221點，跌271點，較上日恒指收市26487點，低水266點。科指期貨夜市收報5001點，較上日科指收市低水61點；國指期貨夜市收報8851點，較上日國指收市低水93點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15903377-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be130%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e6%99%ae%e5%81%8f%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e9%80%be1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-22 08:14:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段跟隨美股回吐 日經暫跌0.46% 韓市跌0.35%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華爾街股市昨晚回吐，日韓股市今早初段亦跟跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250807_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250807_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時07分，日經平均指數跌273點或0.46%，報59075點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫跌22點或0.35%，報6366點。</p>\n</div>",
